net.cnri.repository.ref

Class DigitalObjectReferenceCounter

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.cnri.repository.ref.DigitalObjectReferenceCounter

  • public class DigitalObjectReferenceCounter
extends java.lang.Object
    Counts references by object handle to DigitalObjects and Data Elements. Override unreachable(String) to perform an object automatically when a handle has no extant references.
